title: Dark Reign - December
description:
All the comics from Marvel's Dark Reign storyline that came out in December '08.

I saw that there wasn't a torrent on TPB collecting these as a set yet and I figured this kind of thing would be useful for someone who has just finished reading Secret Invasion and wants to get started in on Dark Reign.

I didn't scan any of these comics so all credit goes to the original scanners and uploaders.

Secret Invasion: Dark Reign (one-shot)
Secret Invasion: Requiem (one-shot)
Secret Invasion: War of Kings (one-shot)*
Avengers: The Initiative #20
New Avengers #48
Invincible Iron Man #08
War Machine #01
Ms. Marvel #34
Dark Reign: New Nation (one-shot)


This is my first upload so any feedback/constructive criticism would be greatly appreciated.

*War of Kings isn't technically part of Dark Reign, but it ties up loose ends from the Inhumans Secret Invasion arc, so I figured, what the hell...
